            "text_rmNDTx": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Hi, I’m Maria Flouris- founder of Just a little Sweeter, where every lolly gift box and jar is made with love, a dash of nostalgia, and a whole lot of joy.</p><p>My journey started not with a grand business plan, but a simple, sweet love for everything lollies. Ever since l was a little girl, lollies made me happy-not just the taste, but the colours, smell, the sparkle in people’s eyes when they received some and the way it bought people together. For me, lollies weren’t just treats…. they were tiny, magical moments that brought people together and made everyday moments into something special.</p><p>That love has never faded for me. Over the years l found myself creating lolly boxes for friends and family-birthday surprises, party favours, thank you gifts. Every time people would light up. That’s when l realised: this little act of sweetness could become something bigger.</p><p>So Just a little Sweeter was born- an online lolly store designed to help people send - smiles in the form of beautifully presented, joy-filled treats.</p><p>Here we don’t just sell lollies. We create sweet, memorable experiences. We believe that every gift should feel personal-especially the sweet ones. From our signature lolly mixes to custom keepsake cubes and beautifully wrapped jars, every item is thoughtfully crafted to delight, surprise and spread a little sugar - coated happiness. </p><p>Whether you’re celebrating a milestone, thanking someone special, or sending a sweet “thinking of you”, our creations are made to leave a lasting (and delicious) impression.</p><p>Each order is made with our own special touch - with heart, wrapped with care, and designed to make your day <em>Just a little Sweeter</em>. Whether you’re after a classic favourite or something unique, we make it easy to create a one-of-a-kind gift that’s bursting with personality (and sugar!).<br/><br/></p>",
